---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Concrete Work | J&C Asphalt — Utah Valley"
  description="Concrete curbs, gutters, sidewalks, and flatwork throughout Utah Valley. J&C Asphalt handles concrete work as part of complete paving projects."
>
  <section class="service-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-label">Additional Services</span>
      <h1 class="section-title">Concrete Work &amp; Flatwork</h1>
      <p>Curbs, gutters, sidewalks, and custom flatwork to complement your asphalt project or stand alone. One contractor, complete job.</p>
      <div class="hero-ctas">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Get a Quote</a>
        <a href="/work" class="btn-outline">See Our Work</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-pad">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="overview-inner">
        <div>
          <span class="section-label">Concrete Services</span>
          <h2 class="section-title">One Crew. Both Materials.</h2>
          <p>Many asphalt jobs also require concrete work — curbs, gutters, borders, or aprons. Rather than coordinating two separate contractors, J&amp;C Asphalt handles both, keeping your project on one timeline and one invoice.</p>
          <ul class="service-list">
            <li>Concrete curbs and gutters</li>
            <li>Sidewalks and walkways</li>
            <li>Concrete aprons and approaches</li>
            <li>Flatwork pads and slabs</li>
            <li>Decorative concrete borders</li>
            <li>Concrete repair and replacement</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary" style="margin-top: 2rem; display: inline-block;">Request a Concrete Quote</a>
        </div>
        <div>
          <img
            src="https://placehold.co/560x480/1A1A1A/F5B800?text=Concrete+Work"
            alt="Concrete curb and gutter installation by J&C Asphalt"
            width="560"
            height="480"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-pad section-dark">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="combo-callout">
        <div class="combo-text">
          <span class="section-label">Better Together</span>
          <h2 class="section-title">Asphalt + Concrete in One Project</h2>
          <p>Most driveways and parking lots benefit from concrete curbing or bordering. Handling both materials with one crew eliminates scheduling conflicts, reduces costs, and produces a cleaner final result.</p>
          <p>When you work with J&amp;C Asphalt, your entire project — asphalt and concrete — gets done by one professional team on one coordinated timeline.</p>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn-outline-yellow" style="margin-top: 1.5rem; display: inline-block;">Talk to Our Team</a>
        </div>
        <div class="combo-image">
          <img
            src="https://placehold.co/520x420/1A1A1A/F5B800?text=Combined+Project"
            alt="Asphalt and concrete combined driveway project by J&C Asphalt"
            width="520"
            height="420"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-pad">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-label">Recent Work</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">Concrete Projects</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="mini-gallery">
        {[1,2,3].map(n => (
          <img
            src={`https://placehold.co/560x380/1A1A1A/444444?text=Concrete+Project+${n}`}
            alt={`Concrete project ${n} by J&C Asphalt`}
            width="560"
            height="380"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="service-cta">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Ready for a Concrete Quote?</h2>
      <p>Whether it's standalone concrete work or part of a larger paving project, we'll get you a fast, free estimate.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary" style="background:#000; color:#F5B800;">Get a Free Quote</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .service-hero {
    padding: 8rem 0 5rem;
    background-color: #111111;
    border-bottom: 3px solid #F5B800;
  }

  .service-hero h1 { font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem); margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem; }
  .service-hero p { color: #888; font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.7; max-width: 600px; margin-bottom: 1.75rem; }
  .hero-ctas { display: flex; gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .section-pad { padding: 5rem 0; }
  .section-dark { background-color: #111111; }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 580px;
    margin: 0 auto 3rem;
  }

  .overview-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 5rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .overview-inner h2 { margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem; }
  .overview-inner > div > p { color: #888; font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .overview-inner img { width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }

  .service-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.6rem;
  }

  .service-list li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #B0B0B0;
  }

  .service-list li::before {
    content: '';
    width: 18px;
    height: 18px;
    background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width='18' height='18' viewBox='0 0 18 18' fill='none' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cpath d='M3 9l4 4 8-8' stroke='%23F5B800' stroke-width='2' stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-position: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .combo-callout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 5rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .combo-text h2 { margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem; }
  .combo-text p { color: #888; font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .combo-image img { width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }

  .mini-gallery {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .mini-gallery img { width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }

  .service-cta {
    background-color: #F5B800;
    padding: 5rem 0;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .service-cta h2 {
    font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3vw, 2.75rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #000;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .service-cta p {
    color: rgba(0,0,0,0.7);
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    max-width: 480px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .overview-inner, .combo-callout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 3rem; }
    .mini-gallery { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 580px) {
    .mini-gallery { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
